# This directory is populated by `flux bootstrap github` (or equivalent).
# It will end up containing:
#   - gotk-components.yaml  (the four Flux controllers)
#   - gotk-sync.yaml        (GitRepository + Kustomization "flux-system")
#   - kustomization.yaml    (kustomize bundle of the above)
#
# See ../../../../docs/gitops-flux.md for the bootstrap command.
